# ==============================================================================
# CLOUD TRAINER DEPENDENCY MANIFEST (V12.0.6)
# Implementation: Surgical UV-Ready Requirement Baseline
# 
# Purpose:
#   Delineates the core Python environment required for NASA N-CMAPSS 
#   Bayesian RUL training. Optimized for reproducibility and binary parity.
#
# Rationale:
#   - ML Core: Pinned to PyTorch 1.1x / Lightning 1.6 to ensure compatibility 
#     with the validated Bayesian research code.
#   - Cloud Ops: Minimalist GCP integration (Storage only) for artifact sync.
#   - Versioning: Strict pinning to prevent runtime regressions during scale-out.
# ==============================================================================

